  "title": "Copper Nugget",
  "description": "Adds Copper Nugget",
  "body": "<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VJ8xxkl.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/missing-nugget\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/699596?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/coppernugget\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/coppernugget?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p>This Fabric mod adds the Copper Nugget. Copper is the only metal in Minecraft without its nugget.</p>\n<p><strong>How does it work?</strong></p>\n<p>You can obtain Copper Nuggets by smelting <strong>Cut Copper Blocks</strong> and <strong>Lightning Rods</strong> or by crafting them from <strong>Copper Ingots</strong>:</p>\n<h5><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OooLuL6.gif\" alt=\"\" height=\"200\" /> <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jI1krKO.png\" alt=\"\" height=\"202\" /></strong></h5>\n<p>And from these Copper Nuggets you can craft Copper Ingots:<br /></p>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/hDrIsLT.png\" alt=\"Crafting a Copper Ingot from 9 Copper Nuggets\" height=\"200\" /></center>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mars-the-planet.github.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/a1a13adf-7c67-48f1-8d6e-e08334434df1.png\"/></a></p>\n",
